content:
@everyone, SEB pushed a new update this morning that advanced VM detection.

Until further notice, don't use it on SEB.

Patch will likely come out in the next few days.

@everyone  IMPORTANT NOTE FOR RESPONDUS USERS:

To get it working for Respondus, YOU HAVE TO RUN THE CUSTOMIZER POWERSHELL SCRIPT!

Also, it is going to say something about your date time not being correct, simply go into the settings inside of the VM, and mess with the datetime and timezone sync settings

@everyone , new tutorial video for Evadus+ on the Youtube channel, sorry if I'm slow to respond to anyone, I've got the flu

<#1362037965668487238> is going to be the new channel for showcasing tutorials.

I am going to be remaking the tutorial video for Evadus, not happy with how it turned out

@everyone , Gemini 2.5 Pro is now fully functional!

For those curious why this took so long (5 days), it's because it's VERY poorly documented on how to switch to the new Google AI SDK, which is required to use Gemini 2.5 Pro. Despite it being almost 7 months since GA (General availability), it has the most abominable documentation ever.

But alas, it is done, thank fuck.
